{"tid":575650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：預算案已相當關顧基層","createTime":"2018-02-28T10:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T11:26:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61cdce2ffba9bc94369ce11d3bffd4e8d83a5f81","tid":575650,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180228/large/1519808125_3da6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180228%2Flarge%2F1519808125_3da6.jpg&h=69c9201c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於《預算案》沒有公屋免租和全民派錢，被指是「厚中產、薄基層」，財政司司長陳茂波解釋，錢要用得其所，預算案已派出40%盈餘，與特定目標群眾分享經濟成果，「好多市民直接間接都可以受惠到」，其餘則用來投資未來和改善服務，會較為合適。被問到是否意味其任內都不會派錢，他則指要每次評估。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，去年度的盈餘主要來自土地和印花稅收入，考慮到外圍環境等因素，認為今次預算案的盈餘分配已較平衡和合適，又否認並非只將盈餘注資到基金而不動用，強調預算案有措施惠及基層，形容已「相當關顧」他們。<br />\n<br />\n被問到政府幾乎年年有盈餘，為何不索性減稅收，而非只是退稅，陳茂波認為，現時本港稅率相比境外各地仍有競爭力，故他不打算減稅，即使要減，也傾向考慮針對個別行業，提供稅務優惠，繼而促進社會發展。<br />\n<br />\n至於建議大增公務員編制，陳指很多部門反映人手不足，認為「錢到」之餘，還要「人到」，而且開設高官職級，要由立法會批准，他認為已有足夠監察，並無意圖建立「大政府」。"},{"pid":"02dbdd0a5c1a922907a350ecbbec812832f76af8","tid":575650,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a4a2f1216ead0582d0fd80c8fa9da1b24044f3","tid":575650,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6278704886b3c0e82a33dc4ef4558fbac37cfa9","tid":575650,"uid":90601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"去海洋公園住？<br />\n去DSE考場訓？"},{"pid":"74b8d34de0d5b2969f8e79959e995979beff3ae3","tid":575650,"uid":5006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"中產係社會支柱，有功有勞默默耕耘<br />\n基層係咩？<br />\n<br />\n連登仔唔係敵視新移民同南亞裔嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：預左對預算案無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf8fec46921cd625f510ede9172136ea7f17832","tid":575650,"uid":55494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:26:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee5f7ab62f16951638f175396ff02faeaa91429","tid":575650,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:26:24.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體無害"},{"pid":"721699e1d8e025fa79112ddc09b61cc796c2edaa","tid":575650,"uid":65686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"基層：已相當想問候陳茂波"},{"pid":"57e7788d2a7c8ef111ea7aa2b4caa2fb1fbbc22b","tid":575650,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"真係好基 廢老新移民 唔攞哂去堆填都算 仲派錢比佢地"},{"pid":"7664f50b5ac7af368f1fffdd009f7f5bdde5e54c","tid":575650,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中產係社會支柱，有功有勞默默耕耘<br />\n基層係咩？<br />\n<br />\n連登仔唔係敵視新移民同南亞裔嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：預左對預算案無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n薯片果啲先無料到<br />\n柒頭波依啲直頭弱智<br />\n海洋公園同DSE免費係咪睇中學雞group project抄番黎"},{"pid":"dff99d632e08f5ee812e213e98f6fef6489b7fda","tid":575650,"uid":13215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"至於建議大增公務員編制，陳指很多部門反映人手不足，認為「錢到」之餘，還要「人到」，而且開設高官職級，要由立法會批准<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個叫你請高官 仲請多幾個垃圾搵幾廿萬?"},{"pid":"7b4d94468d20870053cb2ea5a436862b7b28a6dc","tid":575650,"uid":14083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"今年對中產幾好"},{"pid":"3cfe6dd76161f2fc14dc73eaf289dac3dd3376ab","tid":575650,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:58:42.00